attack.
Released the control of the Nest Stone!

\C[2]I controlled this Nest Stone with magic!
\C[1]The nearby enemies became docile!

Wow! Thank you so much! I was really struggling to
break this with my own strength.

It seems like my comrades are being taken care of!
I'm happy!

This is my way of saying thank you! Thank you very
much!
I'm glad it seems like everyone is safe.

Thank you very much! If it's alright with me, can
I be of help? Please consider me as your comrade!
I'm saved! Please take care of me.
That's good. Nice to meet you.
\c[6]A new loli-mon has joined our party!

This isn't an ordinary key, it's sealed with
magic. There might be some kind of mechanism.

A loli character with the ability to use the Idiot
Strength skill destroys a rock!

It seems like they can destroy rocks if they can
use it.
Is this the wall that Dark was talking about?
Is this the wall that Dark was talking about?

Konoha-san! This person here is the one who
insulted me! I absolutely won't forgive them!

Yay! Thanks to you, I was able to defeat them...!
Ah... I feel like I've become really strong...!

Konoha-san! Please make me a part of the battle
team!
